  "title": "Banana Tree - Stardew Valley Wiki",
  "description": "The Banana Tree is a type of fruit tree. The sapling can be purchased at the Island Trader for 5 Dragon Teeth, found in a Golden Coconut when broken, or as a reward from Large Animal collection in Island Field Office. It takes 28 days to grow to maturity, after which it will produce one Banana each day during the Summer in Stardew Valley or year-round on Ginger Island or in the Greenhouse. It can only grow in the center of a 3x3 square, each square of which must be kept completely clear of objects, flooring, and terrain features. The 3x3 grid must not overlap the 3x3 grid of another Fruit Tree.",
